== 製作 ==
2020年1月，宣佈[[大衛·歐·羅素|大衛·歐·羅素]]將編劇和執導一部由[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]主演，{{le|攝政娛樂公司|Hyperobject Industries}}製片的電影，拍攝預計於4月開始進行<ref name="Russell">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/christian-bale-david-o-russell-movie-new-regency-1202833158/|title=David O. Russell And Christian Bale In Talks For Big Film At New Regency|date=2020-01-16|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr.|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2020-01-16|archive-date=2020-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117050853/https://deadline.com/2020/01/christian-bale-david-o-russell-movie-new-regency-1202833158/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月，[[瑪格·羅比|瑪格·羅比]]和[[麥可·B·喬丹|麥可·B·喬丹]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/margot-robbi-christian-bale-david-o-russell-new-regency-film-1202857952/|title=Margot Robbie To Co-Star Opposite Christian Bale In David O. Russell New Regency Film|date=2020-02-11|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2020-02-11|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212174906/https://deadline.com/2020/02/margot-robbi-christian-bale-david-o-russell-new-regency-film-1202857952/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-b-jordan-joins-christian-bale-david-o-russell-drama-1278703|title=Michael B. Jordan Joins Margot Robbie in David O. Russell Drama (Exclusive)|date=2020-02-12|first=Mia|last=Galuppo|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=2020-02-12|archive-date=2020-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200212193116/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michael-b-jordan-joins-christian-bale-david-o-russell-drama-1278703|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，喬丹因行程衝突退出電影，該角色改由[[約翰·大衛·華盛頓|約翰·大衛·華盛頓]]飾演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/john-david-washington-david-o-russell-film-christian-bale-margot-robbie-new-regency-tenet-1234595019/|title=John David Washington Joins Christian Bale & Margot Robbie In David O Russell Film For New Regency|date=2020-10-09|first=Justin|last=Kroll|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2020-10-09|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010080924/https://deadline.com/2020/10/john-david-washington-david-o-russell-film-christian-bale-margot-robbie-new-regency-tenet-1234595019/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月，宣佈[[雷米·馬利克|雷米·馬利克]]、[[柔伊·莎達娜|柔伊·莎達娜]][[勞勃·狄尼洛|勞勃·狄尼洛]]、[[麥克·邁爾斯|麥克·邁爾斯]]、[[提摩西·奧利芬|提摩西·奧利芬]]、[[麥可·夏儂|麥可·夏儂]]、[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]、[[安雅·泰勒-喬伊|安雅·泰勒-喬伊]]、[[安德莉亞·瑞絲柏|安德莉亞·瑞絲柏]]、[[馬提亞斯·修奈爾|馬提亞斯·修奈爾]]和[[亞歷桑德羅·尼沃拉|亞歷桑德羅·尼沃拉]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/rami-malek-zoe-saldana-david-o-russell-new-regency-1234672072/|title=Rami Malek & Zoe Saldana Join David O. Russell Film At New Regency|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2021-01-13|accessdate=2021-01-13|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113164803/https://deadline.com/2021/01/rami-malek-zoe-saldana-david-o-russell-new-regency-1234672072/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Deadline">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/robert-de-niro-mike-myers-timothy-olyphant-michael-shannon-chris-rock-anya-taylor-joy-david-o-russell-new-regency-movie-1234674307/|title=Robert De Niro, Mike Myers, Timothy Olyphant, Michael Shannon, Chris Rock, Anya Taylor-Joy & More Join David O. Russell Movie|date=2021-01-14|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115003545/https://deadline.com/2021/01/robert-de-niro-mike-myers-timothy-olyphant-michael-shannon-chris-rock-anya-taylor-joy-david-o-russell-new-regency-movie-1234674307/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月，[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒·斯威夫特]]被透露作為演員陣容之一<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/taylor-swift-david-o-russell-1234961503/|title=Taylor Swift Set for David O. Russell Movie|date=2021-06-01|first=Mia|last=Galuppo|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=2021-06-01|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601204618/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/taylor-swift-david-o-russell-1234961503/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
